ABSTRACT
[Object] To provide a wireless communication device and a
wireless communication method capable of further reducing
power consumption in a wireless node. [Solution] Provided
is a wireless communication device including a wireless
communication unit configured to transmit a signal to a base
station through wireless communication, a positional infor-
mation acquisition unit configured to acquire positional
information indicating a position of the wireless communi-
cation device, and a control unit configured to determine an
area to which the wireless communication device belongs
based on the positional information acquired by the posi-
tional information acquisition unit and control the wireless
communication unit to perform the transmission according
